Company Description                    




                        Cigniti Technologies Limited, formerly Chakkilam Infotech Limited, engages in the development of computer software and services to ISVs and enterprise information technology organizations. The company offers functional testing, performance testing, and test automation services. Cigniti Technologies' services portfolio includes software product testing, testing for enterprise information technology, test consulting, outsourced product development, medical transcription, and engineering services in CAD/CAM/CAE. Incorporated in 1998, the company is based in Hyderabad.                    


