IT Consulting & Services

Computer Software




Company Description


Cigniti Technologies Ltd. engages in the development of computer software and services. It offers software testing services, which include quality engineering, advisory and transformation, next generation testing, and core testing. The company was founded by Venkata Chakkilam Subramanyam and Sudhakar Pennam on September 3, 1998 and is headquartered in Hyderabad, India.




Website


http://www.cigniti.com






